  <h1 class="gd-h1">Iceland Heliskiing Operators, Compared</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Several operators fly the same extraordinary corner of North Iceland. They differ far more on <em>how</em> you ski it — format, lodging and price — than on the mountains themselves. Here is an honest look at the field and how to choose, before you see <a href="/packages">the packages</a> or read more on <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
